<p>GLP-1 Effective Weight Loss Therapy For Diabetes Patients</p>
<p>Editor's ChoiceAcademic JournalMain Category: Obesity / Weight Loss / Fitness</p>
<p>Also Included In: Endocrinology;  Diabetes</p>
<p>Article Date: 11 Jan 2012 - 8:00 PST</p>
<p> email to a friend    printer friendly    opinions   </p>
<p></p>
<p></p>
<p></p>
<p></p>
<p></p>
<p></p>
<p></p>
<p><!--</p>
<p></p>
<p>google_ad_client = 'pub-1971793357249522';</p>
